{
  "stem": "10181.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember if there was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I know that a lot of things he did, and he was, more or less, the leader of the community in many ways.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as I could remember, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I said, I couldn't go out and play.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I played with other kids, but it was-- after a while, it became dangerous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, of course, when the time came to go to school-- to kindergarten-- go to school, we couldn't anymore because Jewish kids could not go to the same school as-- as other kids.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they had established a Jewish school, which I went to.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now, I-- I guess the community must have been big enough to support-- it was a small school, but it-- it-- it supported a school.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't know whether-- I'm sure they got a few Jewish families in little villages in the area.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They probably came there, too, I imagine.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I remember the name of the teacher, even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, there was a teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He lived-- he was the gentleman who lived-- who rented a room from my mother.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he taught.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was the teacher there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I think there's only one teacher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I don't remember anybody else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Might have been teacher's aids, but I don't-- don't remember them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I remember the-- the orphanage much better than I remember the school, OK, because it sort of, I guess, left more of an impression on me, being organized.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it was, you know, [? even ?] [? nice ?] to go to [? there ?] [? now. ?] Also, all the-- now that I remember, when I think about it, the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You asked me before about the Jewish holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
